But it's a narrow case about Americans.
And that's the framework of discourse here.
You shouldn't accept it, I don't think.
In fact, take another Obama case-- one
of Obama's major attacks on civil liberties.
It's a case that probably most of you haven't heard about,
but I'd look it up if I were you.
It's a nice thing about the internet.
