The group happened to be the PKK-- Kurdish group.
The US government calls it a terrorist group,
so it's on the terrorist list.
Humanitarian Law Project was giving legal advice to them.
Obama's Justice Department decided
to condemn that as material assistance to terrorism.
Material assistance of terrorism used
