But, you know, it is a topic that could be studied.
It is being studied, in fact.
But as far as I know, there are no real results,
and I think it would be surprising,
because it's all kind of superficial.
It does add a kind of superficiality
to life, which may not be a good thing.
I think it's probably harmful in the long run.
